Musio: Those are both great things! What do you think is the most challenging part of the class?

User: For me, it's understanding all the grammar rules. There are so many of them!

Musio: Yes, grammar can be tricky. But you're doing a good job with it, right? Just keep practicing and you'll get better and better at it.

